                    android:layout_height="2dp"
                    android:background="#6D8FB2" />

                <TableRow
                    android:layout_width="wrap_content"
                    android:layout_height="wrap_content" >

                    <TextView
                        android:layout_width="wrap_content"
                        android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                        android:padding="15dp"
                        android:text="•About 22 Acres pollution free Lush Green Campus on National Highway having excellent modern infrastructure.\n\n•2.75 Lacs sq. ft. built up area.\n\n•Highly qualified &amp; experienced faculty from IIT/NIT/Universities/Industries.\n\n•Regular interaction with reputed industries/ institutions/ IITs.\n\n•LCD, LED, OHP, Multimedia projector equipped classrooms.\n\n•Industry oriented skill development programmes.\n\n•MOU signed with NIIT to impart training for students in latest technologies according to industry norms.\n\n•Fully air conditioned Campus.\n\n•Well equipped CS,IT,EC,Civil,EE labs and Workshops.\n\n•Daily lecture notes on individual students e-mail ID.\n\n•Merit based scholarship.\n\n•Dynamic training and placement cell.\n\n•Indoor &amp; Outdoor Playgrounds for all Games.\n\n•24 - hours All round security with CCTV cameras in campus.\n\n•R.O. water supply."
